The plague that happened didn't have anything to do with a quest though. It started in a raid encounter. Usually it would be over shortly after the encounter. However, in this case a player or pet was brought into a high population area where it spread to players who could not even access that encounter. Once in that dense population it spread uncontrolably and because characters would die and come back only to be rerinfected and killed by it, it had nearly unlimited hosts.
