quote:Originally posted by katoth:I think that there are a lot of interesting possibilities with this. Primarily around other non-lethal but annoying effects of diseases. I agree, it's going to have to be annoying and persistent after death, which is worse than lethal in WoW.Maybe you just plain sneeze all the time, maybe it gives you the 'drunk' effect? Whatever, it can't prevent you from fighting (I don't think making you weaker would go down well with players) and there's got to be a process you can go through to get the cure that takes a bit of time. I think infection must be visible to players and others within a few minutes, or it will be too hard to control.Maybe they put magic gates up at the entrances to certain areas that won't let you through if you are infected and make it part of the storyline.
